  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tiny moves, building big picture stuff!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the simple magic of combining three matching tiles to make your city bigger and better. With an added sprinkle of strategy. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Town with Unique Themes!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.poster.avif?t=1728655970\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.webm?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.mp4?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our variety of themes lets you build a town in your ideal aesthetic, including festive options like Halloween and Christmas! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have we mentioned night mode?</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.poster.avif?t=1728655970\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.webm?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.mp4?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a dark mode gremlin? Us too! Switch to Night Mode and watch as your city grows & glows under the stars. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No rush</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No timers or stress. Merge, build, and expand at your pace, crafting your city your way. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chill Out with our Lo-Fi Tunes and Low-Poly Art</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tiny moves, building big picture stuff!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the simple magic of combining three matching tiles to make your city bigger and better. With an added sprinkle of strategy. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize Your Town with Unique Themes!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.poster.avif?t=1728655970\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.webm?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/20adc6e71e581d1b3b1e4f0d48677452.mp4?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our variety of themes lets you build a town in your ideal aesthetic, including festive options like Halloween and Christmas! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have we mentioned night mode?</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.poster.avif?t=1728655970\" width=608 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.webm?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2715700/extras/da5dd4fd8919c132190a1ebfecbc2660.mp4?t=1728655970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a dark mode gremlin? Us too! Switch to Night Mode and watch as your city grows & glows under the stars. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No rush</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No timers or stress. Merge, build, and expand at your pace, crafting your city your way. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chill Out with our Lo-Fi Tunes and Low-Poly Art</strong></p></li></ul>",
